{"tid":391377,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【歹毒冒犯】吳克儉：大專生自殺因欠規劃","createTime":"2017-09-07T17:23:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T05:06:21.000Z","uid":11001,"like":51,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c938f102382b212891c34fdde632625f85865ed9","tid":391377,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:23:48.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】教育局局長吳克儉（圖）昨引防止自殺委員會報告內容，指大專生自殺源於未做好生涯規劃，又稱大專生在壓力下「有啲唔舒服嘅嘢就頂唔順」，言論引來譁然。委員會成員之一的港大學生會會長孫曉嵐質疑吳說法與小組建議有偏離，「唔理解佢點解會落呢個結論」。立法會議員游蕙禎則指「生涯規劃」荒謬，認為政府需認清問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161015/19801599\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161015%2F19801599&d=WhmYtBF9Rnlk5MCaoV2acMP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=bb94c44f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161015%2F19801599&h=0e676c91\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161015/19801599</a>"},{"pid":"3987f9cb2fe2f512c259a0bebfca68099b8875d5","tid":391377,"uid":11001,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:25:36.000Z","msg":"大專校長當時又有冇譴責吳克儉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1290ec22dbe289e344074fcaffafbfc4d57e121f","tid":391377,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T17:28:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大專校長當時又有冇譴責吳克儉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n直頭要列入通輯名單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6525bbf533129771c37074198ba11a8e24e0b824","tid":391377,"uid":37874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T18:07:45.000Z","msg":"教育局唔該回應下呢篇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9deb1db996a74b49a2cbd5885a41e635860697","tid":391377,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor